sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Premium User
    participant FE as React<br/>ReportsPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>ReportExportView
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant PDF as WeasyPrint

    U->>FE: Click "Export PDF" on report
    FE->>API: GET /api/reports/{id}/export/
    API->>DB: Report.objects.get(pk=id)
    DB-->>API: Report instance with data
    API->>PDF: Render HTML template with report data
    PDF-->>API: PDF binary content
    API-->>FE: 200 OK (application/pdf) Content-Disposition: attachment
    FE-->>U: Browser downloads report PDF
